criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy status

          -  Age: 18-45

          -  Normal weight (BMI 18.5-24.9) who voluntarily accept to join the study, after informed
             consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  <18 Years;

          -  Pregnancy and lactation;

          -  Systemic disorders;

          -  Dietary supplements intake (vitamins, antioxidants, botanicals, phytochemicals)

          -  Abnormal hematological parameters;

          -  Heavy smoking and alcohol drinking;

          -  High-intensity physical activity.
